sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Gateway
    participant HTTP as caikit Runtime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    participant gRPC as caikit Runtime<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP
    participant Registry as Module Registry
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(Remote)
    participant Embed as EmbeddingModule
    participant Peft as PeftPromptTuning
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>(Remote)
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformer<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant FS as Filesystem<br/>/caikit/ mount

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/models/model:predict
    KServe->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    HTTP->>Registry: Dispatch to module
    Registry->>TextGen: Python in-process call
    TextGen->>HFModel: PyTorch inference<br/>(CausalLM / Seq2SeqLM)
    HFModel-->>TextGen: Generated text
    TextGen-->>HTTP: GeneratedTextResult
    HTTP-->>KServe: JSON response
    KServe-->>Client: Prediction response

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation Inference

    Client->>KServe: POST /v1/models/model:predict
    KServe->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    HTTP->>Registry: Dispatch to module
    Registry->>TextGenTGIS: Python in-process call
    TextGenTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationRequest<br/>TLS (optional) / mTLS (optional)
    TGIS-->>TextGenTGIS: GenerationResponse
    TextGenTGIS-->>HTTP: GeneratedTextResult
    HTTP-->>KServe: JSON response
    KServe-->>Client: Prediction response

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 3: Embedding Inference

    Client->>KServe: Embedding request
    KServe->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    HTTP->>Registry: Dispatch to module
    Registry->>Embed: Python in-process call
    Embed->>STModel: SentenceTransformer.encode()<br/>Thread-safe tokenization
    STModel-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
    Embed-->>HTTP: EmbeddingResult
    HTTP-->>KServe: JSON response
    KServe-->>Client: Embedding response

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 4: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training

    Client->>gRPC: Training request<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    gRPC->>Registry: Dispatch to training method
    Registry->>Peft: PeftPromptTuning.train()
    Peft->>HFModel: Load base model<br/>(CausalLM / Seq2SeqLM)
    HFModel-->>Peft: Model loaded
    Peft->>Peft: PEFT prompt tuning<br/>GPU/CPU via Accelerate
    Peft->>FS: Save prompt vectors<br/>(encoder.pt, decoder.pt)
    FS-->>Peft: Vectors saved
    Peft-->>gRPC: Training complete
    gRPC-->>Client: Training response
